1
00:00:05,980 --> 00:00:08,507
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,507 --> 00:00:12,162
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,162 --> 00:00:18,255
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,255 --> 00:00:24,481
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,481 --> 00:00:30,702
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,702 --> 00:00:35,988
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:35,988 --> 00:00:43,088
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,088 --> 00:00:48,312
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,312 --> 00:00:49,916
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,916 --> 00:00:55,579
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,579 --> 00:01:02,088
♫ Every day the sun shines through the window ♫

12
00:01:02,088 --> 00:01:08,655
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,655 --> 00:01:11,802
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:20,970 --> 00:01:24,259
Bin, don't forget what you promised me.

15
00:01:24,259 --> 00:01:27,740
Don't worry. I'll definitely make sure everything is perfect.

16
00:01:27,740 --> 00:01:29,999
Make sure everything is perfect.

17
00:01:33,490 --> 00:01:35,860
Reporter Niu!

18
00:01:35,860 --> 00:01:38,020
You're finally here.

19
00:01:38,020 --> 00:01:40,619
I'm the No. 3 High School's coach of the pre-Olympic Track and Field Team, Gao Bin.

20
00:01:40,619 --> 00:01:43,522
If you see any inadequacy, please advise us.

21
00:01:50,460 --> 00:01:53,900
Reporter Niu, you see, we'll fully cooperate with you.

22
00:01:53,900 --> 00:01:57,199
- You can film however you want.
- That's right.

23
00:01:57,199 --> 00:02:00,359
We have 30 athletes on the team, right?

24
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,820
We currently have 20.

25
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:05,099
- Can they all come?
- Most likely.

26
00:02:05,979 --> 00:02:13,600
- We'll come back another day.
- No, don't! Reporter Niu, you see, since you're already here, just shoot it today.

27
00:02:14,379 --> 00:02:18,899
I originally wanted to shoot a large group of track and field athletes

28
00:02:18,899 --> 00:02:23,159
running across your field, looking youthful and enthusiastic.

29
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:27,780
I'll then pair it with the music from Chariots of Fire, (British historical sports film) to make it more solemn and majestic.

30
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:31,199
That would be such a nice promotion for your No. 3 High School.

31
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:33,800
But you don't have enough people right now. What should I film?

32
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:37,739
It's not that I don't want to shoot it, I can't achieve that result.

33
00:02:38,339 --> 00:02:39,619
Reporter Niu, that's...

34
00:02:39,619 --> 00:02:42,819
Reporter Niu, I think your idea is wonderful.

35
00:02:42,819 --> 00:02:44,779
Wait right here. I'll go gather people for you.

36
00:02:44,779 --> 00:02:49,839
See? He's going to gather people. How about this? Let's film the school campus first, all right?

37
00:02:49,839 --> 00:02:53,340
Look at this statue. It looks so nice, right?

38
00:02:53,340 --> 00:02:58,040
Isn't it beautiful? Especially the dove in its hand...

39
00:02:58,040 --> 00:03:00,680
Xiaowen, you don't have to force yourself so hard.

40
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:04,000
Even if you don't want to spend Gao Bin's money, my mom has money.

41
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,140
What's our relationship? How can I spend your mom's money?

42
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:09,279
- Aren't we brothers?
- Who's brothers with you?

43
00:03:09,279 --> 00:03:11,239
What do you mean by that?

44
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:16,499
Even if you make it to the national competition, you'll only get the scholarship if you're in the top three.

45
00:03:16,499 --> 00:03:19,959
It will be our senior year soon. When will you have time? Who do you think you are?
(T/N: China only has 3 years of high school)

46
00:03:19,959 --> 00:03:21,939
You don't think I can do it?

47
00:03:24,230 --> 00:03:27,519
Mr. Gao, I'm not going! I'm listening to music!

48
00:03:27,519 --> 00:03:29,539
You have to go! It's an emergency.

49
00:03:29,539 --> 00:03:33,259
- Gao Bin, let go of Jiabao.
- You're here right in time. Come on.

50
00:03:33,259 --> 00:03:36,699
Xiaowen, come with us, too. The Track and Field team is assembling together. You little rascal, stop pulling on my pants!

51
00:03:36,699 --> 00:03:39,008
[Episode 16: Don't Want To Think Whether the Future Will be Flat or Muddy]

52
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:57,200
Cut! Stop filming.

53
00:04:03,460 --> 00:04:05,919
Reporter Niu, What's wrong?

54
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:10,319
Why is there a student wearing earrings?

55
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:11,259
- That one.
- Which one?

56
00:04:11,259 --> 00:04:13,560
That one! That one!

57
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,599
Piao Jiutong, take off your earring!

58
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:18,259
- I just stuck them on.
- Take it off!

59
00:04:19,020 --> 00:04:21,940
Jiabao, take off your headphones.

60
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:28,080
Reporter Niu, look.

61
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:30,240
Is this our track and field team?

62
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,659
Yes, yes.

63
00:04:31,659 --> 00:04:34,199
There are tall, short, fat, and skinny ones here.

64
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:38,039
After we film it, how would that look harmonious?

65
00:04:38,039 --> 00:04:40,320
I knew Gao Bin would be unreliable.

66
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:46,020
Reporter Niu, here's the thing. Well, they're

67
00:04:46,020 --> 00:04:49,060
in different events.

68
00:04:51,580 --> 00:04:53,820
Different events?

69
00:04:53,820 --> 00:04:56,240
This boy, what is he training for?

70
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,299
I'm training to be a street dancer.

71
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:04,560
No, don't! That kid is just kidding! He's just kidding!

72
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,859
Piao Jiutong, stop sprouting nonsense.

73
00:05:06,859 --> 00:05:10,200
He's training for... gymnastics.

74
00:05:12,140 --> 00:05:13,740
Gymnastics?

75
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:15,560
What exactly are you training for?

76
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:18,940
Don't talk. What is this kid training in? This boy is training for...?

77
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:20,740
- Me?
- Yes.

78
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:23,740
That's right, Mr. Gao. What am I training for?

79
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:25,600
He's training for

80
00:05:28,220 --> 00:05:31,540
- shot put.
- That's right, shot put.

81
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:33,200
Shot put.

82
00:05:34,770 --> 00:05:37,439
Shot put?

83
00:05:38,099 --> 00:05:42,659
There's a famous Greek discus-thrower statue.

84
00:05:42,659 --> 00:05:47,239
We have a shot putter in Tieyuan.

85
00:05:47,239 --> 00:05:50,300
That'll work! Mr. Gao, go get a shot put.

86
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:52,379
- Okay, okay.
- Hurry!

87
00:05:52,379 --> 00:05:54,080
Kid, come over here.

88
00:05:55,659 --> 00:05:58,179
Kid, quickly come over here.

89
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:02,680
- Strike a pose here.
- Film him.

90
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:05,240
- Please learn from him.
- Strike a shot put pose.

91
00:06:07,460 --> 00:06:10,979
You... Just pretend the videographer doesn't exist. Be more natural.

92
00:06:10,979 --> 00:06:13,040
I got it! I'll just pretend you don't exist.

93
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:17,019
That's right. Come on. Strike a shot put pose. Like this.

94
00:06:17,019 --> 00:06:21,799
Turn around. Three, two, one, throw it!

95
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:32,659
Bin, once we establish the pre-Olympic track and field team, we'll be on TV.

96
00:06:32,659 --> 00:06:35,380
We'll be famous!

97
00:06:35,380 --> 00:06:37,739
Tell me about it.

98
00:06:37,739 --> 00:06:40,660
Old Jin, you have no idea.

99
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:44,520
When I was in Beijing, I checked out so many schools.

100
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:47,219
They do have better facilities.

101
00:06:47,219 --> 00:06:51,919
But we have the best principal!

102
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,260
That's right!

103
00:06:54,260 --> 00:07:00,180
However, no matter how good the principal is, it's the coach who leads well!

104
00:07:00,180 --> 00:07:06,499
It's mainly because we have a brilliant leader! We are thriving under your leadership!

105
00:07:06,499 --> 00:07:08,179
Let me summarize it.

106
00:07:08,179 --> 00:07:10,940
It's only good when it's good for everyone.

107
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,540
That's right!

108
00:07:14,650 --> 00:07:16,359
Keep a low profile.

109
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:18,219
Keep a low profile.

110
00:07:18,219 --> 00:07:21,600
Xiaowen, then you'll have another chance to compete?

111
00:07:22,859 --> 00:07:25,700
That's great! We can compete together again.

112
00:07:25,700 --> 00:07:28,299
Would the final competition be in Beijing?

113
00:07:28,299 --> 00:07:30,979
That's nonsense.

114
00:07:30,979 --> 00:07:33,299
Do you have a brain? If it's not in Beijing, do you think it'll be in Tieyuan instead?

115
00:07:33,299 --> 00:07:37,620
That's nice. We can form a cheerleading squad and go to Beijing together

116
00:07:37,620 --> 00:07:40,000
to cheer for Xiaowen and Mi Jia.

117
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:42,860
You're still going to cheer, Beibei?

118
00:07:42,860 --> 00:07:47,659
Besides, we'll be seniors by then. How would our parents let us go?

119
00:07:47,659 --> 00:07:53,160
We have to go! It's such an important event. We all have to be there! Am I right, Meng?

120
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:57,079
Yes, we'll just say we're going to visit colleges in Beijing. It'll definitely work.

121
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:58,140
That's right.

122
00:07:58,140 --> 00:08:00,340
I think Sister Tian Meng is right.

123
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:02,199
My goodness! Why did you come out again?

124
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:05,620
We're not even taking you along. What are you so excited about?

125
00:08:05,620 --> 00:08:07,320
Seriously.

126
00:08:08,940 --> 00:08:11,060
But then again,

127
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:16,360
if we go to Beijing, I can go visit Wang Cailing.

128
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:18,380
Gao Yang!

129
00:08:18,380 --> 00:08:22,060
Old Jin, all of the footage will be about you later on.

130
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:26,979
You'll all be in there, too.

131
00:08:26,979 --> 00:08:28,219
Look at how happy your dad is.

132
00:08:28,219 --> 00:08:29,820
Gao Yang, are you in there?

133
00:08:29,820 --> 00:08:33,720
Of course, I am! I'm the face of No. 3 High School.

134
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:36,300
It's starting! It's starting!

135
00:08:37,530 --> 00:08:40,219
Demonstrating our vigor as we anticipate the Olympic Games, the students of Tieyuan are in action.

136
00:08:40,219 --> 00:08:42,579
While the entire nation is happily anticipating the Olympic Games,

137
00:08:42,579 --> 00:08:45,839
No. 3 High School of Tieyuan enthusiastically responds to the call by establishing the largest

138
00:08:45,839 --> 00:08:49,140
and strongest High School Track and Field Team of the entire Province.

139
00:08:53,519 --> 00:08:55,720
- That's me!
- Jiabao.

140
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:58,459
- You look quite good on camera.
- The principal is in the background!

141
00:08:58,459 --> 00:09:00,620
Calm down. Calm down.

142
00:09:00,620 --> 00:09:02,759
Poverty alleviation and helping farmers to develop a distinguished economy,

143
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:06,660
featured agricultural products from Dadianzi Village in Dazhuangzi Town of Tieyuan

144
00:09:06,660 --> 00:09:11,039
has attracted consumers to travel from various regions in Northeast China.

145
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:17,780
That's it?

146
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:22,160
Exactly. This... We worked on it all afternoon, and that's it?

147
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:24,759
Dad, where are you?

148
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:27,800
Go back to training.

149
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:29,719
Time to train. We're going back to training.

150
00:09:29,719 --> 00:09:32,420
- Meng, Mi Jia, come feed the rabbit in my room.
- Okay, okay.

151
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:35,139
You're not done with your homework yet. Go do your homework.

152
00:09:38,900 --> 00:09:43,240
Principal, my movement just now, wasn't it accurate?

153
00:09:45,290 --> 00:09:48,500
Beibei, what are you doing? You should have brought me with you.

154
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:38,360
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

155
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:41,920
Wait, why are you here?

156
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:48,000
I overslept! Xiao... Xiao... Xiaowen!

157
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,000
What do you mean Xiaowen? He's almost back already.

158
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:53,020
- You even said you'd take him to train.
- I'm so unreliable!

159
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:55,080
I-It's been so many years since I woke up this early in the morning.

160
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:57,079
I just overslept.

161
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,299
Tomorrow...

162
00:10:58,299 --> 00:11:01,080
Tomorrow, I'll surely go train with him.

163
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,120
Where are you going?

164
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,200
To take a dump.

165
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,000
Can you let me go first? I can't hold it anymore.

166
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:05,962
Go away.

167
00:11:05,962 --> 00:11:08,522
[Jenny's Salon]

168
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:13,779
Jenny, the one on yesterday's news was your son, right?

169
00:11:13,779 --> 00:11:17,339
- What news broadcast?
- Tieyuan News, the one who threw the shotput.

170
00:11:17,339 --> 00:11:20,459
Wait, I must say, Zhao Jiabao. What were you up to instead of going to school this time?

171
00:11:20,459 --> 00:11:21,960
I didn't do anything.

172
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:24,600
She said you were on the news and you threw a shotput?

173
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,900
It originally had nothing to do with me. They were there to film the track and field team.

174
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:30,719
Mr. Gao just had me there to make up the numbers. He forced me to make the headcount.

175
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,480
If you were staying in the classroom like you were supposed to,

176
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,879
would he be able to force you?

177
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:35,480
Did you run out somewhere to play again?

178
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,360
He forced our entire class to do it.

179
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:41,120
I'm telling you, your mom and I are still angry about

180
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:43,780
you going to that singing contest behind us.

181
00:11:43,780 --> 00:11:46,800
Do you think it's really easy to embark on the path of an artist?

182
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:47,980
Exactly.

183
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:49,720
If being an artist was such an easy path,

184
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,539
would your dad and I be here cutting hair?

185
00:11:51,539 --> 00:11:52,939
Seriously.

186
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,240
Alright, I got it.

187
00:11:58,559 --> 00:12:00,380
Hello, is this Zhao Jiabao's house?

188
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:01,699
Brother, are you here for a haircut?

189
00:12:01,699 --> 00:12:03,299
I... No, I'm not here for a haircut.

190
00:12:03,299 --> 00:12:07,279
I'm looking for Jia... Jiabao! Come here. I've finally found you.

191
00:12:07,279 --> 00:12:08,519
Reporter Niu.

192
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,980
Did this boy get in trouble again?

193
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:13,240
No, I'm from the TV station.

194
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:15,080
I want to ask Jiabao to shoot a commercial.

195
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,580
What?

196
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,700
Shoot a commercial?

197
00:12:27,679 --> 00:12:30,360
- Jia.
- Jia, open the door! Quickly!

198
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,840
Jiajia!

199
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,320
Why are you here?

200
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,659
We have something to tell you.

201
00:12:35,659 --> 00:12:36,840
- Quickly come on in.
- Let's go.

202
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,320
Let's go.

203
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,399
- Hello, Auntie.
- Hello, Auntie.

204
00:12:39,399 --> 00:12:40,899
Hello.

205
00:12:40,899 --> 00:12:41,900
Hurry up and come here.

206
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,039
Quickly sit down.

207
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:43,679
No, that's okay.

208
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,879
We have something to show you first.

209
00:12:52,602 --> 00:13:03,902
[Notice for Missing Person]

210
00:13:12,519 --> 00:13:13,919
Auntie,

211
00:13:18,159 --> 00:13:19,959
did you publish this?

212
00:13:20,639 --> 00:13:22,039
Yes.

213
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:24,440
It is published.

214
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,600
Thank you.

215
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:29,120
What is there to thank? We are family.

216
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:32,080
I'm happy if you're happy.

217
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:38,499
Don't cry. You'll certainly find them.

218
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:42,059
Good girl, Jia. You've learned to be coquettish.

219
00:13:46,659 --> 00:13:48,259
Don't cry.

220
00:13:58,299 --> 00:13:59,899
What are you doing?

221
00:13:59,899 --> 00:14:02,239
Nothing. Keep studying.

222
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:20,020
You're going to sleep?

223
00:14:20,020 --> 00:14:21,939
Sleep early, wake up early.

224
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:42,700
I'm not drinking Moutai anymore.
(Chinese distilled liquor using fermented sorghum)

225
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:46,460
Drink.

226
00:14:50,020 --> 00:14:51,860
Gao Bin, time to wake up!

227
00:14:51,860 --> 00:14:53,980
Wake up! Wake up!

228
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:55,699
Wake up!

229
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:03,580
Gao Yang, do you know how old I am?

230
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:05,659
You scared me into almost getting a heart attack.

231
00:15:05,659 --> 00:15:07,860
No more nonsense. Quickly sober up.

232
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:09,600
Time to go train with Xiaowen.

233
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,700
I know.

234
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:17,019
Why did you wake up so early?

235
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:21,239
To supervise you!

236
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:27,080
Wait, Gao Bin, don't just ride the bike. Give him some guidance.

237
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,500
What does our training have to do with you?

238
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:30,980
I'm afraid you'll not take it seriously and slack off so I'm here to supervise you.

239
00:15:30,980 --> 00:15:32,740
I don't need your supervision. Go back home and sleep.

240
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:34,140
I'm not sleepy.

241
00:15:34,140 --> 00:15:35,540
Hurry up.

242
00:15:45,039 --> 00:15:46,279
Xiaowen, what's wrong with him?

243
00:15:46,279 --> 00:15:47,720
He's been like that for days.

244
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,600
Does he really think he's Sleeping Beauty?

245
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:53,199
He's been following me during my morning runs.

246
00:15:53,199 --> 00:15:55,804
You're the one competing. Why is he following along?

247
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:00,240
Exactly. I didn't ask him to wake up early. He just insists on following along.

248
00:16:01,140 --> 00:16:02,940
He cares about you.

249
00:16:04,179 --> 00:16:06,140
Classmates!

250
00:16:06,140 --> 00:16:09,200
Quickly come look at this!

251
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,500
Hurry up and close it!
[Dadianzi Village's Agricultural Products]

252
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:14,240
- I just took it from my dad's office!
- Come back here! Put it away!

253
00:16:14,879 --> 00:16:17,399
He's a star!

254
00:16:18,570 --> 00:16:20,170
- Hurry up and take it!
- Stop running!

255
00:16:20,170 --> 00:16:22,630
My goodness!

256
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:23,920
Don't! Don't!

257
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,420
Stop running!

258
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:27,879
We have a star in our class!

259
00:16:27,879 --> 00:16:28,642
Put it down!

260
00:16:28,642 --> 00:16:29,985
[If You Want To Live In a Mansion, Sweet Potatoes Will Make You Rich]

261
00:16:31,485 --> 00:16:33,827
[Dadianzi's Hogs Are Big and Strong]

262
00:16:38,819 --> 00:16:41,900
Stop looking at it! Hurry up and eat the sweet potatoes, okay? Hurry.

263
00:16:45,399 --> 00:16:50,200
Your poster is quite high-tech. A shotput can even turn into a sweet potato.

264
00:16:52,059 --> 00:16:55,680
I've trained you for so many years. You're finally a star now.

265
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:56,919
I didn't want to do it.

266
00:16:56,919 --> 00:16:58,919
My parents forced me to do it.

267
00:16:58,919 --> 00:17:02,359
They performed dance opera for so many years and no one asked them to be a spokesperson.

268
00:17:02,359 --> 00:17:04,300
Then... Then how much did they pay you?

269
00:17:05,279 --> 00:17:07,319
30 catties (15kg) of pork, and 100 catties (50kg) of sweet potatoes.

270
00:17:07,319 --> 00:17:10,079
When you finish, you each take a case home.

271
00:17:10,079 --> 00:17:11,480
Wait a minute.

272
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:15,100
Say the endorsement slogan on the poster for us again.

273
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:17,019
Aren't they all written on the poster?

274
00:17:17,019 --> 00:17:18,419
Hurry up!

275
00:17:18,419 --> 00:17:19,920
If you want to live in a mansion,

276
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:22,400
sweet potatoes will make you rich.

277
00:17:24,176 --> 00:17:26,219
Stop. Stop laughing.

278
00:17:26,219 --> 00:17:28,199
I can't control it!

279
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,460
Stop laughing!

280
00:17:33,359 --> 00:17:35,180
Stop laughing, all of you!

281
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:42,720
Dadianzi hogs are big and strong.

282
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:45,120
Jin Beibei, stop laughing!

283
00:17:52,599 --> 00:17:54,199
Watch and learn.

284
00:17:57,839 --> 00:17:59,420
So easy.

285
00:18:01,359 --> 00:18:02,839
Xiaowen,

286
00:18:02,839 --> 00:18:04,680
since I'm so talented,

287
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:05,960
if I can get into the NBA

288
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,000
and become an NBA star,

289
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:10,319
what agricultural products should I endorse?

290
00:18:10,319 --> 00:18:13,359
The NBA stars are all college graduates.

291
00:18:23,939 --> 00:18:25,539
Dawei,

292
00:18:28,599 --> 00:18:31,320
- is your wound getting better?
- I'm fine.

293
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:34,060
The college entrance exams are coming up. Are you still in the mood to play basketball?

294
00:18:34,060 --> 00:18:36,000
How is that any of your business?

295
00:18:38,939 --> 00:18:40,619
Good luck with your college entrance exam!

296
00:18:42,079 --> 00:18:43,679
Good luck.

297
00:18:50,620 --> 00:18:54,779
Dawei is... not a bad person.

298
00:19:05,259 --> 00:19:06,659
Two to zero.

299
00:19:09,300 --> 00:19:11,539
Jiajia, pick one for me.

300
00:19:12,620 --> 00:19:14,320
This one looks nice.

301
00:19:21,039 --> 00:19:23,019
No, this makes me look too mature.

302
00:19:23,019 --> 00:19:27,080
I want a pair that's bright, colorful, and young. The type that is suitable for young girls.

303
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:33,579
- What about this one?
- This one is nice.

304
00:19:33,579 --> 00:19:35,780
These are pretty. There's even a pink one, too.

305
00:19:35,780 --> 00:19:37,320
They're pretty.

306
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:41,520
What do you think, Jiajia?

307
00:19:43,340 --> 00:19:45,059
What's wrong, Jia?

308
00:19:46,319 --> 00:19:47,919
Are you upset?

309
00:19:49,780 --> 00:19:52,519
Beibei, do you think

310
00:19:52,519 --> 00:19:57,840
m-my father would see the notices I posted?

311
00:19:59,559 --> 00:20:01,960
Jiajia, you need to be confident.

312
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:03,910
Think about it, your aunt was able to find you.

313
00:20:03,910 --> 00:20:06,880
You'll definitely be able to find your dad, too. Right?

314
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:12,000
Cheer up. You have to be confident. Come on, smile.

315
00:20:12,979 --> 00:20:15,640
Let's go see Meng. Let's go.

316
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:18,339
Meng, did you find it?

317
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:25,319
They didn't publish yours again?

318
00:20:29,119 --> 00:20:30,219
That's okay.

319
00:20:30,219 --> 00:20:34,080
That means their editor doesn't have good artistic taste.

320
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:35,840
Let's send it to another publisher.

321
00:20:36,780 --> 00:20:39,999
When we haven't succeeded, anything we say sounds like complaints.

322
00:20:41,459 --> 00:20:43,280
Look at Jiabao.

323
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:48,459
Ever since he became a spokesperson, even his parents are starting to encourage him to study music.

324
00:20:48,459 --> 00:20:50,259
What about me?

325
00:20:51,419 --> 00:20:55,120
Then we'll keep sending it to magazines until they publish it.

326
00:21:01,300 --> 00:21:03,859
I'm sorry. I woke up late. Wait for me, okay?

327
00:21:03,859 --> 00:21:05,960
We'll go together later.

328
00:21:11,039 --> 00:21:12,699
The final exams are around the corner.

329
00:21:12,699 --> 00:21:14,780
If you keep following me every day, what are you going to do about your grades?

330
00:21:14,780 --> 00:21:17,079
It's... it's okay. You don't need to worry about it.

331
00:21:17,079 --> 00:21:19,840
I won't worry if you don't fall asleep in class.

332
00:21:21,459 --> 00:21:24,580
What will you do if I can go to college but you can't when the time comes?

333
00:21:24,580 --> 00:21:29,780
If you can get into college, then I can, too. I won't let it affect my studies.

334
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:32,199
I'm being serious with you, Gao Yang.

335
00:21:32,199 --> 00:21:35,119
I'm being serious, too. Don't worry.

336
00:21:35,119 --> 00:21:39,240
Fine, tell me then. How high can you rank in the final exams?

337
00:21:41,780 --> 00:21:45,780
Within the whole grade, I'll advance

338
00:21:46,430 --> 00:21:49,600
five ranks.

339
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:52,419
Thirty places, not five!

340
00:21:52,419 --> 00:21:55,200
Fine, fine. Thirty it is then.

341
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:10,859
G-Gao Yang, you're joining the track and field team too?

342
00:22:10,859 --> 00:22:12,580
No, I'm here to supervise him.

343
00:22:12,580 --> 00:22:13,880
Ignore him.

344
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:15,000
He's just an onlooker.

345
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,000
Who's an onlooker?

346
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:21,440
Well, from now on, I'll be the team leader.

347
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:22,960
I'll take care of the logistics.

348
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:25,859
If anyone's thirsty, remember to come to me for water.

349
00:22:26,499 --> 00:22:28,960
Then you're coming here e-every day?

350
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:29,720
Yes.

351
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:32,759
Won't you be more motivated to train when there's a handsome boy like me here?

352
00:22:32,759 --> 00:22:33,759
Am I right?

353
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:43,140
Assemble, Everyone!

354
00:22:51,079 --> 00:22:53,479
Our track and field team is officially established today.

355
00:22:53,479 --> 00:22:55,900
Go pick up your training plan in my office after school.

356
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:58,499
There are separate plans for group events and specialized events.

357
00:22:58,499 --> 00:23:04,559
All of our sweat today is for next year's National Track and Field Games!

358
00:23:04,559 --> 00:23:05,959
Bravo!

359
00:23:07,599 --> 00:23:09,099
Continue.

360
00:23:12,259 --> 00:23:15,140
I have more good news to share with you.

361
00:23:15,140 --> 00:23:21,060
Since Mi Jia won first place in the last city-wide competition,

362
00:23:21,060 --> 00:23:24,519
she will participate in the provincial boot camp as a representative of Tieyuan.

363
00:23:24,519 --> 00:23:25,819
Applaud!

364
00:23:26,519 --> 00:23:27,919
Applaud!

365
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,380
T-Teacher, h-how long will it be?

366
00:23:34,380 --> 00:23:37,499
A month. It will be led by the provincial team's coach this time.

367
00:23:37,499 --> 00:23:40,860
There will also be a lot of elite athletes and they will use a lot of scientific training methods.

368
00:23:40,860 --> 00:23:43,540
We welcome Mi Jia to share your experience with us when you come back.

369
00:23:43,540 --> 00:23:44,940
Alright,

370
00:23:46,780 --> 00:23:48,959
ten laps of warmups. Start!

371
00:23:54,839 --> 00:23:56,099
One, two, three, four.

372
00:23:56,099 --> 00:23:57,499
Wait, what are you doing?

373
00:23:57,499 --> 00:23:59,319
Let's go. Get up there.

374
00:23:59,319 --> 00:24:00,719
What is it?

375
00:24:02,780 --> 00:24:04,380
Wait, what's the matter?

376
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:09,280
What do you want to say?

377
00:24:10,380 --> 00:24:14,200
Can you not follow me around from now on?

378
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:15,720
What's wrong with following you around?

379
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,999
I've been following you since you were a substitute teacher.

380
00:24:19,060 --> 00:24:21,620
You were only this tall at the time.

381
00:24:21,620 --> 00:24:23,179
How old are you now?

382
00:24:23,179 --> 00:24:25,419
Don't you feel awkward standing right there?

383
00:24:25,419 --> 00:24:28,799
What's awkward about that? I'm the team leader. Why should I feel awkward?

384
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:31,040
Who gave you that title?

385
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:33,400
Well, without me, you can't even be the coach.

386
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:35,180
What's wrong with me being the team leader?

387
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,960
Is it because you don't trust me?

388
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:41,000
You don't think I can train Xiaowen well?

389
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,380
Something like that.

390
00:24:42,380 --> 00:24:44,500
Then what must I do in order for you to trust me?

391
00:24:46,659 --> 00:24:48,259
There's no way I can trust you.

392
00:24:49,019 --> 00:24:52,140
Gao Yang, I'll show you!

393
00:25:06,519 --> 00:25:08,019
Xiaowen,

394
00:25:09,519 --> 00:25:11,680
I'm a bit scared.

395
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:13,259
Scared about what?

396
00:25:13,259 --> 00:25:16,279
Are you afraid that you won't get along with everyone during the boot camp?

397
00:25:16,279 --> 00:25:18,019
No.

398
00:25:18,019 --> 00:25:22,159
Auntie p-published a notice to find my parents.

399
00:25:22,939 --> 00:25:25,059
But the boot camp will take a month.

400
00:25:25,059 --> 00:25:29,739
What if my dad comes home when I'm away? What if we missed each other?

401
00:25:29,739 --> 00:25:31,720
If your dad really comes home,

402
00:25:31,720 --> 00:25:34,559
he'll wait a whole year for you, let alone a month.

403
00:25:34,559 --> 00:25:35,880
Really?

404
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:37,340
Don't worry and just go.

405
00:25:37,340 --> 00:25:40,320
We have to get good results in the national competition this time.

406
00:25:42,259 --> 00:25:44,939
This systematic training is very important for you.

407
00:25:44,939 --> 00:25:49,080
Besides, Auntie will be happy if you achieve great results, too.

408
00:25:51,259 --> 00:25:53,359
I understand.

409
00:25:53,359 --> 00:25:55,219
I'll train very hard.

410
00:26:00,559 --> 00:26:04,120
It'll be nice if you can come with me.

411
00:26:05,720 --> 00:26:07,039
Don't worry,

412
00:26:07,039 --> 00:26:09,000
It's also quite nice to be training with Mr. Gao.

413
00:26:10,459 --> 00:26:12,059
Let's work hard together.

414
00:26:14,799 --> 00:26:16,619
- I'll go train.
- Okay.

415
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:42,420
- Jiajia, are you really going to the boot camp during summer vacation?
- Yes.

416
00:26:43,340 --> 00:26:46,159
I think it'll take a month.

417
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:52,020
Then that means we won't be able to see the concert together.

418
00:26:54,580 --> 00:26:58,400
How about this? I'll go watch it myself and get his signature for you.

419
00:26:58,400 --> 00:27:00,459
Really?

420
00:27:00,459 --> 00:27:02,340
You're so nice, Beibei!

421
00:27:02,340 --> 00:27:04,780
It's nothing. We're besties.

422
00:27:04,780 --> 00:27:07,080
W-Wait a minute.

423
00:27:07,080 --> 00:27:11,080
The final exams are around the corner. Are you sure you can improve by 30 places?

424
00:27:11,080 --> 00:27:13,760
Wait, final exam?

425
00:27:13,760 --> 00:27:15,819
- 30 places?
- Yes.

426
00:27:19,319 --> 00:27:20,880
Where are you going, Xiaowen?

427
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:22,319
I'm going to run.

428
00:27:22,319 --> 00:27:23,799
Didn't you just finish training?

429
00:27:23,799 --> 00:27:25,499
I want to enhance my training.

430
00:27:25,499 --> 00:27:27,000
Wait a minute.

431
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:28,939
Look at this.

432
00:27:28,939 --> 00:27:33,519
I specifically made this specialized training plan just for you.

433
00:27:33,519 --> 00:27:36,080
From Monday to Sunday,

434
00:27:36,080 --> 00:27:38,859
from your shoulders and head to your hip,

435
00:27:38,859 --> 00:27:41,160
I'll be training you in all aspects.

436
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:42,759
After the summer vacation,

437
00:27:42,759 --> 00:27:47,239
you'll surely be a whole new person.

438
00:27:56,599 --> 00:27:59,799
Mommy, are you tired?

439
00:28:01,319 --> 00:28:02,160
Have a seat.

440
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:03,039
What's this?

441
00:28:03,039 --> 00:28:05,480
I'll give you a massage. Take a seat.

442
00:28:06,459 --> 00:28:07,640
You want to give me a massage?

443
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:09,399
Fine, go ahead.

444
00:28:10,799 --> 00:28:11,720
Harder.

445
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,920
Okay.

446
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:13,880
Does that feel good?

447
00:28:13,880 --> 00:28:14,880
It's fine.

448
00:28:20,259 --> 00:28:25,059
Mom, how is Dad's mood lately?

449
00:28:25,059 --> 00:28:27,179
Why are you asking this? Did you cause trouble again?

450
00:28:27,179 --> 00:28:28,920
No, I didn't!

451
00:28:29,799 --> 00:28:33,480
I was just thinking about going to watch a concert during summer vacation.

452
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:35,519
Didn't your dad already agree?

453
00:28:35,519 --> 00:28:40,599
Didn't he say you can go watch the show if you improve by 30 places during this exam?

454
00:28:41,319 --> 00:28:45,240
Mom, what if I can't improve by 30 places?

455
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:46,900
What?

456
00:28:47,860 --> 00:28:50,380
Jin Beibei, even I'm getting angry when I hear that.

457
00:28:50,380 --> 00:28:53,219
Your current grades are already at the bottom of your grade!

458
00:28:53,219 --> 00:28:57,079
How hard is it to advance 30 places from the bottom?

459
00:28:57,079 --> 00:29:01,659
Mom, I made some observations. There are a lot of elites among the poor students.

460
00:29:01,659 --> 00:29:03,219
They are all working really hard now.

461
00:29:03,219 --> 00:29:05,490
If they improve, wouldn't I still be at the bottom?

462
00:29:06,300 --> 00:29:07,599
I...

463
00:29:07,599 --> 00:29:10,759
Jin Beibei, let me tell you. Don't let your dad hear that, understand?

464
00:29:10,759 --> 00:29:13,580
If your dad hears that, he'll die of anger!

465
00:29:13,580 --> 00:29:16,640
I... Go... go away!

466
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:19,679
Mom, just let me go.

467
00:29:19,679 --> 00:29:21,580
I'm not doing it for myself this time.

468
00:29:21,580 --> 00:29:23,060
I'm doing this for Mi Jia!

469
00:29:23,060 --> 00:29:25,319
I already promised to get signatures for her.

470
00:29:25,319 --> 00:29:26,780
Go ask your aunt for signatures.

471
00:29:26,780 --> 00:29:29,659
I have to relay the atmosphere of the show to her, too.

472
00:29:29,659 --> 00:29:32,279
You can also relay the atmosphere if you watch it on TV.

473
00:29:32,279 --> 00:29:35,760
If you're doing this for Mi Jia, then do well on the exam!

474
00:29:37,279 --> 00:29:39,040
- No...
- Seriously, this child!

475
00:29:39,040 --> 00:29:42,080
- Mom!
- Don't whine. Lift your foot! Life your foot!

476
00:29:42,080 --> 00:29:43,719
Go away!

477
00:29:46,860 --> 00:29:48,870
This child! Why are you getting upset?

478
00:29:48,870 --> 00:29:52,820
[Specialized Events Training Plan]

479
00:29:55,699 --> 00:29:57,299
What's wrong, Xiaowen?

480
00:29:57,299 --> 00:29:58,979
Just ask me if there's anything you don't understand.

481
00:29:58,979 --> 00:30:00,480
I'll explain it to you.

482
00:30:14,450 --> 00:30:16,179
You... what do you mean by this?

483
00:30:16,179 --> 00:30:19,600
I want to increase the amount of this training.

484
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:23,279
Xiaowen, training harder doesn't mean better results.

485
00:30:23,279 --> 00:30:25,060
You have to take it step by step, understand?

486
00:30:25,060 --> 00:30:27,499
The provincial boot camp is about to start.

487
00:30:27,499 --> 00:30:30,940
I'm afraid if I don't increase my training, I'll fall behind.

488
00:30:33,019 --> 00:30:36,619
Xiaowen, you have to trust me.

489
00:30:36,619 --> 00:30:41,919
If there's no trust between the coach and the athlete, we won't achieve any results.

490
00:30:41,919 --> 00:30:43,979
Do you understand? You have to trust me.

491
00:30:43,979 --> 00:30:46,660
Then this Dadianzi Village is...?

492
00:30:46,660 --> 00:30:48,800
It'll be the entrance exams in a few days. No. 3 High School is the exam location.

493
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:53,540
You don't have to go to class. I thought you should soak in a hot spring.

494
00:30:53,540 --> 00:30:55,459
After that, we can proceed with—

495
00:30:55,459 --> 00:30:56,400
What are you doing?

496
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:59,179
What hot spring? Soaking in a hot spring? Is this the right time to soak in a hot spring?

497
00:30:59,179 --> 00:31:04,040
What do you know? Am I finished yet? Butting in loudly again.

498
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:09,990
The hot spring will be a special training event. You'll know when you get there.

499
00:31:09,990 --> 00:31:11,470
[Day 5: Insider, Dadianzi Village]

500
00:31:23,079 --> 00:31:26,179
What do you think, Xiaowen? Not bad, right?

501
00:31:26,179 --> 00:31:27,779
Look at these roads underneath your feet.

502
00:31:27,779 --> 00:31:31,540
They are all winding mountain roads at 30 to 45-degree angles.

503
00:31:31,540 --> 00:31:33,380
They are the best to increase your stamina.

504
00:31:33,380 --> 00:31:38,179
After you finish this course, the normal roads will feel like nothing.

505
00:31:38,179 --> 00:31:40,799
After you run, you can soak in the hot spring and relax your muscles.

506
00:31:40,799 --> 00:31:42,200
You'll continue running tomorrow.

507
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:44,759
Before, you said you were afraid the amount of training was not enough.

508
00:31:44,759 --> 00:31:48,400
Now, I'm just afraid you can't finish them.

509
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:51,159
Thank you, Mr. Gao. I will surely complete it.

510
00:31:51,159 --> 00:31:54,219
Don't thank me yet. You're going to hate me later.

511
00:31:54,219 --> 00:32:00,239
Although I normally joke around with you guys, I'm very ruthless when it comes to being a coach.

512
00:32:00,239 --> 00:32:01,979
Don't worry.

513
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:04,580
Go ahead.

514
00:32:04,580 --> 00:32:06,259
Do you want to sing a song?

515
00:32:06,259 --> 00:32:08,760
Go ahead.

516
00:32:08,760 --> 00:32:11,400
♪ I came from the mountains ♪

517
00:32:11,400 --> 00:32:14,760
♪ with an orchid in my hands ♪

518
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:16,820
♪ I plant it in the small garden ♪

519
00:32:16,820 --> 00:32:18,039
- Xiaowen!
- Xiaowen!

520
00:32:18,039 --> 00:32:20,740
- Xiaowen!
- Xiaowen!

521
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:24,580
Gao Yang, why are you here?

522
00:32:24,580 --> 00:32:26,259
I'm asking you, why are you here?

523
00:32:26,259 --> 00:32:27,640
I'm here to supervise you!

524
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:29,419
I don't need you to supervise me!

525
00:32:29,419 --> 00:32:30,979
Beibei, why are you guys here too?

526
00:32:30,979 --> 00:32:32,540
We're here to have fun!

527
00:32:32,540 --> 00:32:34,839
Does Old Jin know?

528
00:32:34,839 --> 00:32:39,740
- Yes, he does! He does.
- We're leaving! There's no room in the car. We'll see you in the village, okay?

529
00:32:39,740 --> 00:32:41,880
- Bye!
- Bye!

530
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:18,750
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

531
00:33:18,750 --> 00:33:25,915
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

532
00:33:25,915 --> 00:33:32,105
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

533
00:33:32,105 --> 00:33:38,145
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams into my heart ♫

534
00:33:38,145 --> 00:33:44,897
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

535
00:33:44,897 --> 00:33:50,437
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

536
00:33:50,437 --> 00:33:54,350
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

537
00:33:54,350 --> 00:33:57,772
♫  Let set sail on our dreams  ♫

538
00:33:57,772 --> 00:34:01,067
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

539
00:34:01,067 --> 00:34:05,727
♫  Even if you stumble and fall  ♫

540
00:34:05,727 --> 00:34:07,835
♫  I'll be by your side  ♫

541
00:34:07,835 --> 00:34:11,038
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

542
00:34:11,038 --> 00:34:15,250
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

543
00:34:15,250 --> 00:34:18,970
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

544
00:34:18,970 --> 00:34:26,930
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
